-- Ally Financial Reports $462 Million Settlement With Fannie Mae
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2010-12-27T21:02:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-27/rescap-reaches-462-million-settlement-with-fannie-mae-over-loan-exposure.html
Ally Financial Inc. said its
mortgage unit, Residential Capital LLC, reached an agreement
with Fannie Mae to resolve potential repurchase exposure for
breaches of selling representations and warranties. The
settlement was for about $462 million.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
